00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:46,060
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:49,440
Jiu?

4
00:02:01,130 --> 00:02:01,920
Jiu?

5
00:02:16,050 --> 00:02:17,100
Sister Pei!

6
00:02:18,230 --> 00:02:19,260
Sister Pei.

7
00:02:22,270 --> 00:02:23,190
Sister Pei.

8
00:02:25,460 --> 00:02:26,440
Don't kill her.

9
00:02:26,760 --> 00:02:28,820
You really care about her, don't you?

10
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:30,100
I just don't think

11
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,460
you should alert them.

12
00:02:38,090 --> 00:02:38,880
After all,

13
00:02:40,940 --> 00:02:43,000
our target is Zhao Yuanzhou.

14
00:02:43,590 --> 00:02:44,850
I'll wait for it to dry.

15
00:02:49,170 --> 00:02:50,410
Just a small patch is wet.

16
00:02:50,410 --> 00:02:51,610
Why bother?

17
00:02:55,530 --> 00:02:56,550
Bai Jiu,

18
00:02:57,550 --> 00:02:59,530
we need to check your wrist.

19
00:03:30,660 --> 00:03:32,610
I am indeed from Chongwu Camp.

20
00:03:40,350 --> 00:03:42,530
You're very curious, aren't you?

21
00:03:44,030 --> 00:03:45,800
Yes, I am.

22
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:50,230
When did he start to seal my five senses?

23
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:55,690
You each take one.

24
00:03:55,880 --> 00:03:58,600
I made these detoxification pills myself.

25
00:03:58,860 --> 00:03:59,840
Taste.

26
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:07,630
What do you want from me?

27
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:09,450
This is the new version of Huanling Powder I developed.

28
00:04:09,450 --> 00:04:10,520
Are you ready?

29
00:04:13,440 --> 00:04:14,360
Smell.

30
00:04:16,240 --> 00:04:17,610
I feel nothing.

31
00:04:17,890 --> 00:04:19,800
I even want to laugh.

32
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:25,220
I'm so scared.

33
00:04:25,590 --> 00:04:27,010
Sight.

34
00:04:27,090 --> 00:04:29,130
Then why are you covering my eyes?

35
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,790
Cover your own eyes.

36
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,180
I can't see the road.

37
00:04:33,210 --> 00:04:34,150
It's so scary.

38
00:04:34,170 --> 00:04:35,270
What's that sound?

39
00:04:35,290 --> 00:04:36,590
Put this on.

40
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:39,190
I think something is definitely wrong with this voice.

41
00:04:39,190 --> 00:04:40,130
Don't listen.

42
00:04:40,470 --> 00:04:41,450
Hearing.

43
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:51,130
I never expected that seemingly harmless Little Bunny

44
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:54,090
could be so meticulous.

45
00:04:54,750 --> 00:04:56,350
To accomplish great things,

46
00:04:56,390 --> 00:04:58,520
one must not only have deep foresight

47
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:01,420
but also patience

48
00:05:02,570 --> 00:05:04,490
to set up the game step by step.

49
00:05:05,220 --> 00:05:06,530
Zhao Yuanzhou,

50
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:10,440
from the moment you entered Tiandu City,

51
00:05:11,390 --> 00:05:12,710
you have been stepping into this chessboard,

52
00:05:12,710 --> 00:05:14,670
bit by bit.

53
00:05:15,390 --> 00:05:18,280
Where do you think the list of these five people

54
00:05:18,350 --> 00:05:20,080
in the vanguard squad formed by

55
00:05:21,190 --> 00:05:23,280
the Demon Hunting Bureau came from?

56
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:26,160
Didn't Mr. Zhuo make it?

57
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,470
So it was you.

58
00:05:33,860 --> 00:05:35,840
To obtain your inner core,

59
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:38,360
we must seal your five senses.

60
00:05:39,580 --> 00:05:42,300
Bai Jiu could do that for me.

61
00:05:42,909 --> 00:05:44,950
However, he lacks experience

62
00:05:45,409 --> 00:05:47,980
and needs someone to protect him.

63
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,360
Ms. Pei,

64
00:05:51,650 --> 00:05:53,390
you don't think our Chongwu Camp

65
00:05:53,390 --> 00:05:54,790
is a place you can enter

66
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:56,600
or exit at will, do you?

67
00:05:57,030 --> 00:06:00,090
You deliberately arranged for me to leave Chongwu Camp

68
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,630
and then be noticed by the Demon Hunting Bureau.

69
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:05,030
Ms. Pei, not only are you a good archer,

70
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:08,360
but you are also the bodyguard of the Prime Minister.

71
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:11,360
Moreover, you have a grudge against Chongwu Camp.

72
00:06:11,710 --> 00:06:12,790
Who else would

73
00:06:12,790 --> 00:06:14,650
the Demon Hunting Bureau choose

74
00:06:15,580 --> 00:06:17,840
besides an outstanding talent like you?

75
00:06:19,470 --> 00:06:22,870
Besides, you just suffered the loss of your younger brother.

76
00:06:23,430 --> 00:06:24,590
When facing Bai Jiu,

77
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:27,720
would there be any emotional projection?

78
00:06:27,770 --> 00:06:29,850
Over time, when you grow deep feelings for him,

79
00:06:29,850 --> 00:06:32,380
you will surely risk your life to protect him.

80
00:06:33,460 --> 00:06:36,590
Bai Jiu calls you 'Sister Pei' every day;

81
00:06:38,630 --> 00:06:40,490
you must be enjoying that, right?

82
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:42,550
Despicable.

83
00:06:43,310 --> 00:06:45,400
If Bai Jiu couldn't succeed,

84
00:06:46,270 --> 00:06:48,070
I would still have a backup plan.

85
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:52,400
Even Mr. Zhuo

86
00:06:53,830 --> 00:06:56,240
is one of your pawns.

87
00:06:57,730 --> 00:07:00,350
Zhuo Yichen is the leader of the Demon Hunting Bureau.

88
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:03,280
It was reasonable for him to join the vanguard squad.

89
00:07:03,750 --> 00:07:06,080
Besides, he has the Cloud Light Sword.

90
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:08,510
He's the only one who can kill you.

91
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:11,440
As for Baize Goddess...

92
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,560
I'll cooperate with Li Lun

93
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,550
to help him destroy the Baize Token.

94
00:07:15,550 --> 00:07:17,270
I promise I'll give you

95
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:19,570
Zhao Yuanzhou's inner core.

96
00:07:22,130 --> 00:07:24,300
What about your promise to me?

97
00:07:25,380 --> 00:07:26,070
To merge

98
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:28,550
the Baize Token hidden in you and Wen Xiao,

99
00:07:28,830 --> 00:07:31,110
we naturally need to bind you together

100
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,710
to endure hardships

101
00:07:33,150 --> 00:07:35,280
so that you can understand each other.

102
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:39,100
Now, there's only one last step left

103
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:40,510
to seal your five senses.

104
00:07:42,310 --> 00:07:44,110
I just need to use a silver needle

105
00:07:44,870 --> 00:07:46,550
to seal your touch,

106
00:07:48,110 --> 00:07:50,240
and everything will be accomplished.

107
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:56,290
What does a mortal like you

108
00:07:57,230 --> 00:07:59,430
want with my inner core?

109
00:07:59,590 --> 00:08:01,700
Who wants your foul inner core?

110
00:08:03,250 --> 00:08:04,150
From the beginning,

111
00:08:04,150 --> 00:08:06,610
what I want is always the Ever-Burning Wood.

112
00:08:08,990 --> 00:08:10,500
It's been such a hard journey.

113
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:11,910
I finally found

114
00:08:11,910 --> 00:08:13,070
the Ever-Burning Wood that he wants.

115
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:14,190
It is said that

116
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,930
this is the last piece of Ever-Burning Wood in the world.

117
00:08:16,930 --> 00:08:18,660
We must keep a close watch on it.

118
00:08:21,370 --> 00:08:22,530
Eight years ago,

119
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:25,380
you inhaled

120
00:08:25,730 --> 00:08:28,430
the last piece of Ever-Burning Wood that I had found

121
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:29,760
with great difficulty.

122
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:34,620
I have been looking for you for eight years.

123
00:08:52,090 --> 00:08:53,350
Go ahead, my disciple.

124
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,020
Bai Jiu,

125
00:09:19,540 --> 00:09:21,510
aren't we your friends?

126
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:36,220
Don't come any closer.

127
00:09:37,430 --> 00:09:38,790
I don't want to hurt you.

128
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:43,430
You've already said so much;

129
00:09:44,560 --> 00:09:46,190
how could I possibly

130
00:09:46,190 --> 00:09:48,520
just let Little Bunny stick a needle in me?

131
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:13,040
What's wrong, Zhao Yuanzhou?

132
00:10:14,460 --> 00:10:17,810
It seems like you can't cast your spells.

133
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:35,410
Jiu,

134
00:10:36,230 --> 00:10:37,440
think it through.

135
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,580
Stop.

136
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:11,190
[Book of Rites]

137
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:17,170
As expected, at the critical moment,

138
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:20,180
you still wished for him to live

139
00:12:21,730 --> 00:12:23,190
and didn't want him to die.

140
00:12:28,590 --> 00:12:29,350
Don't worry.

141
00:12:29,830 --> 00:12:31,430
Whether it's Mr. Fan's order

142
00:12:32,150 --> 00:12:33,650
or the Prime Minister's,

143
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:35,610
it cannot suppress me.

144
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:40,610
The only one who can kill Zhao Yuanzhou

145
00:12:40,710 --> 00:12:42,060
is me.

146
00:12:44,230 --> 00:12:46,540
I won't be anyone's executioner.

147
00:12:47,710 --> 00:12:49,030
Well, if we

148
00:12:49,610 --> 00:12:51,280
restore the Baize Token

149
00:12:52,310 --> 00:12:56,310
and are ultimately able to suppress Zhao Yuanzhou's malicious energy,

150
00:12:56,340 --> 00:12:57,670
will you still kill him?

151
00:13:02,190 --> 00:13:03,720
The Yao Water was polluted,

152
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,860
and the Divine Wood went missing.

153
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,160
The "if" you mentioned

154
00:13:09,450 --> 00:13:11,110
seems too distant to hope for.

155
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:14,440
I won't answer such a hopeless hypothetical.

156
00:13:15,010 --> 00:13:16,120
But what if

157
00:13:16,940 --> 00:13:18,560
the hope is not distant?

158
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:21,790
What do you mean?

159
00:13:22,260 --> 00:13:24,210
Zhao Yuanzhou once mentioned to me

160
00:13:24,990 --> 00:13:26,990
that the clues about the Divine Wood

161
00:13:27,350 --> 00:13:28,610
are in Situ's Mansion.

162
00:13:30,030 --> 00:13:31,270
Situ's Mansion?

163
00:13:32,070 --> 00:13:32,950
Mr. Zhuo.

164
00:13:37,660 --> 00:13:38,580
Mr. Situ Ming.

165
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:39,640
Mr. Zhuo,

166
00:13:39,960 --> 00:13:42,310
please take Ms. Wen Xiao away through the back door now.

167
00:13:42,310 --> 00:13:44,470
Mr. Situ, why are you so panicked?

168
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:46,200
What on earth has happened?

169
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:02,910
Zhen Mei,

170
00:14:02,930 --> 00:14:04,080
what are you doing?

171
00:14:07,270 --> 00:14:09,360
Wen Xiao from the Demon Hunting Bureau

172
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:11,090
murdered the Prime Minister,

173
00:14:11,810 --> 00:14:13,400
resisted arrest, and fled,

174
00:14:13,540 --> 00:14:15,000
committing a grave crime.

175
00:14:16,110 --> 00:14:18,460
Chongwu Camp has been ordered to capture her.

176
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:20,590
Those who block the way will be killed.

177
00:14:20,790 --> 00:14:22,110
The Prime Minister was murdered.

178
00:14:22,110 --> 00:14:23,870
Chongwu Camp is here to arrest the criminal.

179
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:25,670
They claimed the murderer is...

180
00:14:27,750 --> 00:14:29,280
is Ms. Wen Xiao.

181
00:14:29,950 --> 00:14:31,270
Utterly absurd!

182
00:14:31,310 --> 00:14:33,170
How could it possibly be Wen Xiao?

183
00:14:33,290 --> 00:14:35,860
Many of the Prime Minister's attendants

184
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:39,380
witnessed Wen Xiao publicly stop the horse.

185
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:46,270
They said that after Wen Xiao got into the carriage,

186
00:14:46,270 --> 00:14:47,930
she brutally killed the Prime Minister.

187
00:14:47,930 --> 00:14:49,590
The blood dripped all the way.

188
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:54,210
All the servants saw with their own eyes

189
00:14:54,560 --> 00:14:55,870
that inside the carriage,

190
00:14:55,060 --> 00:14:58,200
[Book of Rites]

191
00:14:56,170 --> 00:14:58,410
the Prime Minister's body was mutilated.

192
00:14:58,410 --> 00:15:00,160
Wen Xiao was covered in blood

193
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,960
and ran away.

194
00:15:05,470 --> 00:15:06,600
Nonsense!

195
00:15:06,750 --> 00:15:08,350
Wen Xiao was in the Demon Hunting Bureau all night.

196
00:15:08,350 --> 00:15:10,280
All the guards can testify to that.

197
00:15:10,330 --> 00:15:12,160
I was here all night,

198
00:15:12,830 --> 00:15:15,430
being punished with house arrest by my father.

199
00:15:15,640 --> 00:15:16,760
Chongwu Camp

200
00:15:17,050 --> 00:15:18,740
is clearly framing me.

201
00:15:18,770 --> 00:15:19,650
In such a serious event

202
00:15:19,650 --> 00:15:20,780
as the Prime Minister's murder,

203
00:15:20,780 --> 00:15:22,840
they wouldn't casually frame anyone

204
00:15:23,090 --> 00:15:25,350
unless they were absolutely confident.

205
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:26,590
There must be

206
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:28,380
something fishy going on.

207
00:15:29,270 --> 00:15:30,910
The situation is unclear now,

208
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:32,790
and there are a bunch of witnesses on both sides.

209
00:15:32,790 --> 00:15:34,520
We cannot prove our innocence.

210
00:15:34,550 --> 00:15:35,350
Mr. Zhuo,

211
00:15:35,580 --> 00:15:37,950
you should take Ms. Wen Xiao and leave now.

212
00:15:39,580 --> 00:15:41,470
Before Chongwu Camp closes the city gates,

213
00:15:41,470 --> 00:15:43,670
I'll take Wen Xiao and leave the city as soon as possible.

214
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,390
No.

215
00:15:44,810 --> 00:15:46,210
I'm not leaving the city.

216
00:15:46,710 --> 00:15:48,370
They believe I will escape.

217
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:51,790
So, at this moment, Tiandu City

218
00:15:52,050 --> 00:15:53,700
is the safest place.

219
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:55,750
That's true.

220
00:15:55,910 --> 00:15:57,770
But Tiandu City is not that large.

221
00:15:57,830 --> 00:15:59,710
Chongwu Camp has ample forces in Tiandu City.

222
00:15:59,710 --> 00:16:01,720
They could search the entire city in two or three days.

223
00:16:01,720 --> 00:16:02,910
By the time they realize...

224
00:16:02,910 --> 00:16:03,470
So,

225
00:16:03,890 --> 00:16:05,720
Mr. Situ, please shelter me.

226
00:16:07,190 --> 00:16:07,880
What?

227
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:12,300
Urgent matters need flexible solutions.

228
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:13,300
It's not up to you.

229
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:16,390
I'd like to see

230
00:16:17,060 --> 00:16:18,660
who dares to stop me.

231
00:16:19,040 --> 00:16:19,960
I do.

232
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:40,550
[Arrest Warrant]

233
00:16:36,550 --> 00:16:38,500
King Xiang has issued an urgent decree

234
00:16:38,500 --> 00:16:42,430
to capture the true murderer, Wen Xiao, who killed the Prime Minister.

235
00:16:42,950 --> 00:16:45,210
Anyone who dares to obstruct will be regarded

236
00:16:45,210 --> 00:16:47,210
as having committed the same crime.

237
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:51,310
Go in and arrest her.

238
00:17:26,990 --> 00:17:28,280
Commander,

239
00:17:28,430 --> 00:17:29,700
we have searched the entire Demon Hunting Bureau

240
00:17:29,700 --> 00:17:30,960
and haven't found her.

241
00:17:34,750 --> 00:17:36,480
Seal the city gate immediately

242
00:17:36,810 --> 00:17:38,470
and launch a citywide search.

243
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:40,940
Inspect all inns and taverns,

244
00:17:41,950 --> 00:17:44,700
and issue a wanted notice

245
00:17:45,750 --> 00:17:47,750
for the serious criminal, Wen Xiao.

246
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,040
Come out.

247
00:18:21,710 --> 00:18:22,350
Let's go.

248
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:23,150
Go inside.

249
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,920
Mr. Situ, I never expected your home to have such a rustic charm.

250
00:18:31,920 --> 00:18:32,850
Hurry inside.

251
00:18:32,880 --> 00:18:34,280
Don't let others see you.

252
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:40,960
Come on.

253
00:18:57,100 --> 00:18:58,700
What's wrong with that room?

254
00:18:59,110 --> 00:19:00,550
Why is it sealed?

255
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,350
Oh.

256
00:19:03,550 --> 00:19:05,390
That's my wife's bedroom.

257
00:19:05,510 --> 00:19:07,310
She has been bedridden for many years because of her illness

258
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:08,510
and is sensitive to light and wind.

259
00:19:08,510 --> 00:19:10,240
It has been like this for years.

260
00:19:12,220 --> 00:19:13,040
Ms. Wen Xiao,

261
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:13,580
come.

262
00:19:13,610 --> 00:19:14,330
Follow me.

263
00:19:14,950 --> 00:19:15,390
Okay.

264
00:19:38,540 --> 00:19:40,540
Jiu hasn't been home for a long time.

265
00:19:40,550 --> 00:19:42,610
How about you stay in his room for now?

266
00:20:18,110 --> 00:20:18,980
What a coincidence.

267
00:20:18,980 --> 00:20:20,030
You're here too?

268
00:20:21,330 --> 00:20:22,550
You're here too?

269
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:33,170
I didn't expect

270
00:20:34,290 --> 00:20:35,380
it was Bai Jiu.

271
00:20:36,300 --> 00:20:37,110
Yeah,

272
00:20:38,440 --> 00:20:40,300
I didn't expect it was him either.

273
00:20:40,510 --> 00:20:42,200
I actually didn't expect you

274
00:20:42,280 --> 00:20:44,470
to be hunted down across the entire city.

275
00:20:44,470 --> 00:20:45,580
Impressive.

276
00:20:46,240 --> 00:20:48,100
What's so surprising about that?

277
00:20:48,370 --> 00:20:50,500
Since Mr. Situ is willing to take me in,

278
00:20:50,700 --> 00:20:54,390
I can take the chance to investigate the clues about the Divine Wood.

279
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:56,370
It's you guys who are weird.

280
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:58,550
Why are you here?

281
00:20:58,610 --> 00:21:00,590
To find the Divine Wood, of course.

282
