00:34:34,980 --> 00:34:37,449
I've finished reading all the medical books at home.

570
00:34:37,449 --> 00:34:40,159
I'm going out to find the best master to learn from.

571
00:34:40,159 --> 00:34:41,850
One day,

572
00:34:42,350 --> 00:34:43,989
I will definitely cure you.

573
00:35:39,780 --> 00:35:40,750
You are...

574
00:35:41,240 --> 00:35:43,410
I'm the new apprentice.

575
00:35:43,830 --> 00:35:44,870
My name is...

576
00:35:45,030 --> 00:35:45,670
Si...

577
00:35:47,440 --> 00:35:48,450
My name is Bai Jiu.

578
00:35:50,050 --> 00:35:50,900
Master,

579
00:35:50,930 --> 00:35:51,900
really?

580
00:35:51,920 --> 00:35:54,120
Can you really bring my mom back to life?

581
00:35:54,370 --> 00:35:55,940
I promise you

582
00:35:56,030 --> 00:35:57,890
I will bring your mom back to life.

583
00:35:58,360 --> 00:36:00,760
But I need your help with something as well.

584
00:36:00,970 --> 00:36:03,900
Join the vanguard squad of the Demon Hunting Bureau.

585
00:36:04,210 --> 00:36:07,100
I just need you to seal Zhu Yan's five senses.

586
00:36:14,390 --> 00:36:15,930
I know you have a kind heart.

587
00:36:15,960 --> 00:36:17,650
But Zhu Yan is a demon.

588
00:36:17,670 --> 00:36:19,870
Your mother was killed by a demon.

589
00:36:20,060 --> 00:36:22,340
If he isn't eliminated,

590
00:36:22,740 --> 00:36:24,010
there will be

591
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:25,630
more children like you

592
00:36:25,630 --> 00:36:26,960
who lost their mothers.

593
00:36:31,470 --> 00:36:32,510
Jiu,

594
00:36:32,670 --> 00:36:34,230
you really are a fool.

595
00:36:34,310 --> 00:36:36,470
Your mother was not killed by a demon,

596
00:36:36,470 --> 00:36:37,710
nor is she sick.

597
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,720
You were deceived by Wen Zongyu.

598
00:36:43,710 --> 00:36:44,880
Then my mom is...

599
00:36:54,410 --> 00:36:55,640
Mr. Situ,

600
00:36:56,530 --> 00:36:58,390
don't hide it from Jiu any longer.

601
00:38:09,850 --> 00:38:10,710
Where is my mom?

602
00:38:16,740 --> 00:38:17,780
Where is my mom?

603
00:38:25,780 --> 00:38:27,080
This is your mom.

604
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,960
Nonsense.

605
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:36,250
Your father is not talking nonsense.

606
00:38:36,950 --> 00:38:37,930
Your mother

607
00:38:40,240 --> 00:38:41,750
is not human.

608
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:46,370
Your mother, like Ying Lei,

609
00:38:47,060 --> 00:38:48,980
is half god and half demon.

610
00:38:49,480 --> 00:38:51,320
She was born in ancient times.

611
00:38:52,250 --> 00:38:54,020
She's the same age as the gods.

612
00:38:58,280 --> 00:38:59,120
Yes.

613
00:38:59,310 --> 00:39:00,930
Your mother is the descendant of the White Emperor Shaohao

614
00:39:00,930 --> 00:39:02,950
and the Divine Tree of Jianmu.

615
00:39:06,180 --> 00:39:07,480
Her true form shares

616
00:39:07,500 --> 00:39:10,840
the same origin as the Divine Wood that transformed into the power of Baize,

617
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,640
inheriting its spiritual vein.

618
00:39:12,900 --> 00:39:14,870
Therefore, during the Blood Moon eight years ago,

619
00:39:14,870 --> 00:39:16,380
the disappearance of the Baize Token

620
00:39:16,380 --> 00:39:17,790
severely injured her.

621
00:39:17,790 --> 00:39:18,270
Mom!

622
00:39:18,270 --> 00:39:20,430
She was forced to manifest her true form.

623
00:39:20,430 --> 00:39:22,510
Mom!

624
00:39:22,950 --> 00:39:25,030
Mom!

625
00:39:45,550 --> 00:39:47,520
Even if my mom turned into a tree

626
00:39:47,630 --> 00:39:49,290
and returned to her true form,

627
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:51,640
why has she never talked to me

628
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:54,470
or been willing to respond?

629
00:39:56,680 --> 00:39:58,410
With the loss of the Baize Token

630
00:39:59,840 --> 00:40:02,170
and the Goddess absent from her position,

631
00:40:02,530 --> 00:40:04,860
the Wilderness has fallen into disarray.

632
00:40:05,700 --> 00:40:08,290
Therefore, Lord Bai Yan lost her soul

633
00:40:08,890 --> 00:40:10,710
and had no choice but to stay in her true form

634
00:40:10,710 --> 00:40:12,390
in the world.

635
00:40:15,800 --> 00:40:16,670
Mom,

636
00:40:18,160 --> 00:40:19,360
can you hear me?

637
00:40:21,810 --> 00:40:22,420
I...

638
00:40:23,750 --> 00:40:25,260
I'm Jiu.

639
00:40:27,240 --> 00:40:28,380
I'm back.

640
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:36,970
I'm back.

641
00:40:54,920 --> 00:40:57,400
Can my mom return to her original form?

642
00:40:58,480 --> 00:41:00,540
As long as the Baize Token is repaired

643
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:02,840
and the Wilderness is restored,

644
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:05,630
your mother will come back.

645
00:41:09,470 --> 00:41:11,310
Why did no one tell me?

646
00:41:12,430 --> 00:41:14,680
You were too young at that time.

647
00:41:15,110 --> 00:41:15,950
I didn't know

648
00:41:15,950 --> 00:41:17,080
how you would accept

649
00:41:17,370 --> 00:41:19,480
all of this after I told you.

650
00:41:21,070 --> 00:41:23,870
For an ordinary person, it's indeed hard to accept

651
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:26,710
without going through all this.

652
00:41:27,350 --> 00:41:29,680
But Bai Jiu has the right to know the truth.

653
00:41:31,770 --> 00:41:33,180
Although he is young,

654
00:41:33,600 --> 00:41:36,060
he is much more mature than children his age.

655
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:37,940
I believe

656
00:41:38,910 --> 00:41:40,350
that if you had told him

657
00:41:40,370 --> 00:41:41,650
the truth back then,

658
00:41:42,280 --> 00:41:43,840
Jiu would have understood.

659
00:41:45,020 --> 00:41:46,130
If you

660
00:41:46,230 --> 00:41:48,020
had told me the truth earlier,

661
00:41:49,290 --> 00:41:51,950
perhaps I wouldn't have been used by Wen Zongyu.

662
00:41:52,740 --> 00:41:54,240
I'm sorry.

663
00:41:54,260 --> 00:41:55,020
No.

664
00:41:55,870 --> 00:41:57,030
It was my fault.

665
00:41:59,480 --> 00:42:00,460
I'm sorry.

666
00:42:02,670 --> 00:42:03,840
I was wrong.

667
00:42:06,500 --> 00:42:07,590
I'm sorry.

668
00:42:09,120 --> 00:42:10,640
I hurt you guys.

669
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,410
All of you

670
00:42:13,630 --> 00:42:14,960
have been sincere to me,

671
00:42:17,250 --> 00:42:19,130
but I have let down your trust.

672
00:42:20,490 --> 00:42:21,660
Jiu.

673
00:42:42,020 --> 00:42:43,120
Jiu,

674
00:42:43,880 --> 00:42:45,190
you've grown up.

675
00:42:45,960 --> 00:42:47,510
The bond between father and son,

676
00:42:47,510 --> 00:42:49,170
the loyalty between friends,

677
00:42:49,570 --> 00:42:51,630
rights and wrongs, gains and losses—

678
00:42:53,310 --> 00:42:55,340
you can understand them on your own.

679
00:42:58,930 --> 00:43:00,460
It's okay to make mistakes.

680
00:43:02,520 --> 00:43:03,610
As long as

681
00:43:03,640 --> 00:43:05,800
you can bear the cost of growing up

682
00:43:07,120 --> 00:43:08,380
and try to make amends.

683
00:43:14,040 --> 00:43:15,840
The sea of suffering is endless.

684
00:43:16,660 --> 00:43:18,920
As long as you return to the shore in time,

685
00:43:19,320 --> 00:43:22,380
there will still be a brilliant sunset waiting for you.

686
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:31,550
In fact,

687
00:43:32,110 --> 00:43:33,710
the real culprit

688
00:43:34,670 --> 00:43:35,950
is not you, this easily fooled

689
00:43:35,950 --> 00:43:37,270
little bunny.

690
00:43:37,660 --> 00:43:40,270
But the truly cunning and deceitful wolf.

691
00:43:43,430 --> 00:43:44,430
Stop hiding.

692
00:43:44,660 --> 00:43:45,990
Come out.
